A real estate video tour featuring 33229 30th Ave SW Federal Way, WA 98023. 4 BR, 2 3/4 Baths, MLS# 28071349.
Property Description: Property Lines Real Estate presents 33229 30th Ave SW Federal Way, WA 98023.
Amidst the bustle of Federal Way, a convenient location close to town center, easy access to major commuting arteries, come home to an oasis offered by this immaculate split entery in Twin Lakes. The floor plan is great with living areas suitable for entertaining and private areas offering respite from the daily grind. The wood burning fireplace and large windows make the room warm and inviting.
The formal dining room beckons on the right and is perfect for welcoming a party for family and friends. The sliding glass doors lead onto the deck and is an amazing place to relax. The bright and open kitchen provides new appliances all purchased in 2007. All walls in this home have recently been professionally painted. The expansive master bedroom is equipped with large glass windows and has a beautiful view of the back yard. Additional bedrooms can be used as a spacious office or sleeping areas for friends and family.
Unique to this home is a recording/practice room. Because it is soundproofed it can be used as a safe haven for children's active play. The back yard is appointed with a basketball hoop and concrete patio. From the deck enjoy the quiet ambiance of the woods and green space that adjoins providing ultimate privacy. Your yard will stay pristine green with in-ground sprinkler systems in the front and back. The property is partially fenced and is in "move-in" condition, This home is a truly a "must see", and is listed at only $315,000.
